settings.description: You and your crew are on vacation when a anomaly strikes your ship and you and your crew evacuates! You find your ship safe but 4 of your crewmates are missing! Find them! Based off: VVVVVV
A long and vegetable filled adventure. A mini Mario game I guess?
Bowser has taken control of the plains! Defeat his army and claim the plains!
a whole castle filled with bricks that can be turned into koopas and mushrooms? what a dream! course, Bowser's waiting at the end to ruin the fun!
We finish the first world,the next one is in the desert.
basically 1-1/baby steps level from a koopa's revenge 2 but remade in smaghetti
Pick up coins from the ground, and go underground and collect them there
First time I put the raccoon tail power up,enjoy.
